AssetType.name: General Asset
AssetType.description:
Penetrate all general asset type class including solar panels, power lines, telco towers, townships, and many more. Various applications at the tip of your finger, streamlining critical data for smooth operational performance and asset integrity.
|
geoRISE is a one stop solution for a host of features catering to multiple type of assets and industrial applications in asset management.

AssetType.name: Building Asset
AssetType.description:
Monitor and manage your building at any phase of the asset life-cycle. Whether pre-assetization during building construction or even operations & maintenance for building inspection and routine updates. 
|
This will enable comprehensive digital twinning features for robust handling of building management.

AssetType.name: Agriculture Asset
AssetType.description:
Boost your agricultural monitoring activity with online mapping data in RGB or NDVI format. Automate the process to monitor key parameters including AI tree counting for selected crops to offer precise insight of your agricultural land.
|
geoRISE will enable a single digital data platform to show your various agricultural land assets.

AssetType.name: Infrastructure Asset
AssetType.description:
Optimize and enhance your management for any infrastructure asset types including bridges, roads, dams, pipelines, and any other critical asset infrastructure.
|
Monitor and digitalize any asset updates to ensure structural asset integrity and high level performance at every stage of its life-cycle.
